data.description: LIMESTONE SCHOOL DISTRICT! This 4 bedroom, 1 bath home has a ton of potential. You will love the wrap around deck! Home has an open floor plan with living room and kitchen.  Main floor bedroom plus 2 upstairs and 1 in the walk out basement (has 2 egress windows). Home is on corner lot and has off street parking for 1 vehicle.  Property is to be sold AS-IS. Seller will not make any repairs.
